(755, NULL, NULL, 821, 'A006105506D', 'Lead', 'muriuki.wa.muriuki@gmail.com', 'KENYAN', '27870196', '58-10300', 'KERUGOYA', 'KIRINYAGA', '0716721706', '<p align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">COVER LETTER</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>I have a bachelor&rsquo;s degree in environmental planning and management and I completed an internship to learn about environmental concerns. I also gained hands-on experience working in the field as an environmental expert and a GIS expert. I have extensive knowledge of the principles and standards associated with environmental resources in addition to all the environmental laws and regulations that apply having been registered as a NEMA expert, Certification No. NEMA/EIA/RC/3093 and expert registration No. 9733. I also have a good understanding of the scientific, political, ethical and economical sides surrounding environmental issues.</p>\r\n<p>I have the training and skills to conduct research and to collect samples to analyse in order to determine the condition of the environment in specific areas. I can then use the information to create management and restoration plans. I have extensive knowledge of computer diagram and mapping software such as CAD and GIS programs with the ability to create diagrams and schematics to help explain the plans. I also have basic knowledge in surveying and using surveying instrument.</p>\r\n<p>I have the ability to identify environmental problems and to prepare reports or give presentations explaining the issues that need to be addressed. I also have the skills to conduct studies that look at the ecological effects that changes in the environment have on a particular area.</p>\r\n<p>I have excellent verbal and writing skills with the ability to convey information in a clear and effective manner. I have a real concern for preserving the environment as much as possible and the knowledge to help find ways to make a difference.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Thank you,</p>\r\n<p>Alex Muriuki</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
