is was further boosted by the new roles in research teams, being able to inerogate the environmental and social impacts of various products being investigated.</p>\r\n<p>Up to to the pursuit and attainment of my Masters in Project Planning and Management, I had been actively deployed in a projects engineer capacity with cross cutting role in several projects in my institutions of employment since 2015. This multi-disciplinary engagement in multiple projects created the initial requirement to grasp valuable project environmental and social management skill. This was further aided by the continue work in international institutions that continued to require engagement on multiple emerging aspects in the sustainable development of infrastructre projectsprojects.</p>\r\n<p>I remain convince that you shall consider my application.</p>\r\n<p>Your Faithfully</p>\r\n<p>Eng. Tony Mwashuma</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
