(4397, NULL, NULL, 4746, 'N/A', 'Associate', 'aabdulwahab31.aa@gmail.com', 'Kenyan', '32469913', '10', 'Marsabit', 'Marsabit', '0793311159', '<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">I am <strong>Amina Rahma Hussein</strong>. I join EIK as a member so that i nurture my career and expertise in this great institution.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">I was born and raised in <strong>Marsabit County</strong>, a place with a high concentration of pastoralist&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">communities and with an arid climate prone to recurrent droughts.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\"> Despite the fact that&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">successive governments have marginalized the region, resilience and traditional knowledge of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">their environments have helped these communities live and thrive in this &lsquo;harsh&rsquo; climate. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">I am&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">fascinated by the deep traditional knowledge of pastoralists in managing their environment and&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">livestock.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">To further my interest in such environmental knowledge and Natural resource management, I decided&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">to undertake a Diploma course in Environmental Management at the <em>Kenya Wildlife Service Training Institute</em>. I later furthered my education to <em>Kisii university</em> where i persued a Bechelor degree course in Natural resource management.</span><br /><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">&nbsp;</span><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">Being a member of EIK will allow me to gain deeper insights into the legal framework around environmental management as well as natural resource management. On the other hand, I will&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">bring practical experience from the grassroots which I hope will enhance the work of EIK as well as its affiliates.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">In particular, drawing from my previous experience, I will be able to gather evidence of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">environmental impacts, initiate and facilitate discussions with the local state authorities, local&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">communities, NGOs and civil Society Groups.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\">I therefore strongly believe that being a member will have a positive impact in making our environment a better place by engaging and learning more.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\"><strong>Amina Rahma Hussein,</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: \'andale mono\', times; font-size: large;\"><em>BS,Natural Resource Management.</em></span></p>'),
