(4892, NULL, NULL, 5254, '', 'Associate', 'douglasmokua93@gmail.com', 'Kenyan ', '31864655', '40500', 'Nyamira ', 'Nairobi County', '0725683023', '<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"242\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"339\">\r\n<p>Douglas Mokua Environmental Science degree holder with professional skills in Occupational Safety and Health (OSH). Am currently working with Safepro Ltd as a Health, Safety and Environment Supervisor since August to date, tasked to supervise solar intallation project .</p>\r\n<p>Have also worked with CRJE (EA) Ltd at the Business Bay Square (BBS) project in Eastleigh, Nairobi, as a safety officer for 3 years and 8 months.</p>\r\n<p>Mokua wass tasked to implement company&rsquo;s HSE policy to ensure all the site activities adhere to Standard Operating Procedures and safe work procedures. The site holds over 900 workers, both skilled and the unskilled workforce.</p>\r\n<p>Previously have also worked with Africa Waste and Environment Management Centre as a field assistant for a period of seven (7) months where involved in the Environmental and Social Impact assessment study For the 60KM 220Kv Malindi-Kilifi Transmission Line and Substation extension at Malindi Project.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" width=\"581\">\r\n<p>For the last three years have managed to gain hands on skills in OSH management systems including hazard identification and management, accident investigation and reporting, risk assessment and conducting statutory audits and reporting. He is strong team player, excellent networking and communication skills, outstanding report writing and conflict resolution skills. In addition, Douglas has the ability to conduct toolbox talks, develop and and run effective induction programs, conduct safety trainings, basic first aid, fire safety and develop and implement OSH policies and procedures for construction sites.</p