(5029, NULL, NULL, 5404, NULL, 'Associate', 'x', 'KENYAN', '29248091', '1151', 'NAIROBI', 'NAIROBI', '712592732', '<p>I am an experienced Environmental Officer with a passion for environmental sustainability with 4 years of experience in environmental management and conservation. I am skilled in environmental impact assessment, environmental auditing, and environmental policy development. I have a proven track record of developing and implementing environmental management plans and conducting environmental audits to ensure that activities are environmentally sound. I am committed to working collaboratively with other stakeholders, including government agencies, NGOs, and local communities, to address environmental concerns. I am a strong communicator with excellent interpersonal skills and the ability to work effectively in a team environment.</p>'),
