d advocacy in environmental matters. By aligning my aspirations with the institute\'s goals, I am confident that together, we can create a more sustainable and resilient future for our communities and ecosystems.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Thank you for considering my application to join the Environmental Institute of Kenya. I am eager to bring my passion, skills, and dedication to the institute and contribute to its invaluable work in environmental conservation and sustainable development.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Sincerely,&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 7.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">CHRIS MBURU MUGO</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">Environmentalist - KeRRA</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\"><a href=\"mailto:chrismugo80@gmail.com\">chrismugo80@gmail.com</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 115%; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">0705121262</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
