(5047, NULL, NULL, 5424, 'NA', 'Lead', 'rapospat@gmail.com', 'Kenyan', '7023084', '40601-200', 'BONDO TOWN', 'KENYA', '254-721516325', '<p>My name is Prof. Patrick Odhiambo Hayombe, seeking to register as a Lead Expert with the Environment Institute of Kenya.&nbsp; Iam a registered and licenced member with NEMA as Lead Expert (registration no. 0252 and current practising Licence No. NEMA/EIA/EROL/20170. I posses Doctor of Philosophy Degree (2010) and Master of Philosophy Degree in Environmental studies (1997) (Environmental Planning and Management) from Moi University and Bachelor of Arts (Geography, 1989) fron Nairobi University.&nbsp; I have worked as Physical Planning Officer with Ministry of Lands and Settlement, Kenya Water Institute (as Deputy Director and Director). Has worked with Jaramogi Oginga Odinga University (as a Lecturer to Senior Lecturer and currently an a Associate Professor and formerly, the Dean School of Spatial Planning and Natural Resource Management).&nbsp; I have prepared a number of Environmental Impact Assessment and Audit reports. As an academic and researcher I have published in several scientific refereed journals and supervised several post-graduate and undergraduate dessertations in environment related fields. I believe I have the requisite skills to be admitted as a Lead Expert with the Environment Institute of Kenya.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
