(5051, NULL, NULL, 5429, 'N/A', 'Associate', 'njaramba.maureenw@gmail.com', 'KENYAN', '27246839', '425-01000', 'THIKA', 'KIAMBU', '702173547', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">My name is Maureen Wanjiku Njaramba, an environmentalist who graduated in 2012 from Jomo Kenyatta University of Agriculture and Technology with a Bachelor of Science degree in Plant Ecology and Environmental Sciences. I am currently working as a senior regional development officer at the State Department of the ASALs and Regional Development within the Directorate of Regional Development where among my duties include&nbsp;Undertaking activities on protection and sustainable development of riverine lacustrine, oceanic and natural resource base and coordinating Regional Development Agencies&rsquo; activities geared towards conservation, restoration and management of vulnerable and fragile ecosystems</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">I registered with National Environment Management Authority as an associate Expert in 2019. However, I did not register with EIK because back then i was working in a different field. Now that I am in my career path, i wish to register with the institute so i can sharpen my skills as an environmentalist which will enable me to grow in my environmental career. in addition, my career objective is to succeed in an environment of growth and excellence and earn a job which provides me satisfaction and self development and help me to achieve both personal and organizational goals which will go a long way in helping me gain practical exposure, personal growth and development and modeling me to become competitive both nationally and globally, therefore being a member of EIK will enable me to achieve this objective and propel me to greater heights.</p>\r\n<p>I hope to hear from you soon on the approval.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),
