(5058, NULL, NULL, 5436, NULL, 'Associate', 'x', 'Kenyan', '29910755', '432-20103', 'Eldama Ravine', 'Baringo', '254707054852', '<p>Joy Jepngetich Kibet</p>\r\n<p>P.O. Box 432, Eldama Ravine 20103, Kenya</p>\r\n<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:joyeekibet@gmail.com\">joyeekibet@gmail.com</a></p>\r\n<p>Cell phone:&nbsp; +254707054852</p>\r\n<p>Date: 31<sup>st</sup> <sup>&nbsp;</sup>January, 2024</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To</p>\r\n<p>The Registration Team,</p>\r\n<p>Environmental Institute of Kenya,<br /> <strong>P.O.Box:</strong>&nbsp; 5087, Nairobi Kenya</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Ref: Registration for Membership in Environmental Institute of Kenya,</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>I hope this email finds you well. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; My name is Joy Jepngetich Kibet, a master&rsquo;s holder in Environmental Planning and Management from Kenyatta University and Degree holder in Environmental Horticulture and Landscaping Technology from Jomo Kenyatta University of Agriculture and Technology. I am writing to express my interest to be a member of Environmental Institute of Kenya. Working in Eco-Ethics and Development as research assistant in Environmental Impact Assessment (EIA), Environmental and Social Impact Assessment (ESIA) and Environmental Audit (EA) projects enabled me to learn more about the consideration while undertaking EIA, ESIA and EA projects. Additionally, I can analyse a project and identify potential impacts on the environment. Through interaction with different organization both public and private, ensuring compliance to organization&rsquo;s policies, guidelines, procedures and legislations, I am able to answer and resolve any questions related to the organizations operations.</p>\r\n<p>I have successfully completed three years of experience under Eco-ethics and development, which is a registered firm of experts and under the mentorship of Dr, Stephen Njoka Nyaga who is a core director of the company and a registered lead expert. As a master&rsquo;s student in Kenyatta University Perusing Masters of Environmental Planning and Management, I was able to take a course in Environmental Impact Assessment and Audit as part of my curriculum, successfully completed, attained, and mean grade of B. &nbsp;I am well versed with computer skills, statistical tools, mapping tools and software, which will help in coordination, and ensuring critical analysis in order to make informed decisions. Additionally, my skills in Environmental Impact Assessment (EIA), Environmental and Social Impact Assessment (ESIA) and Environmental Audit (EA) have enabled me to write reports related to the projects and improve on my skills.</p>\r\n<p>I am particularly interested in the being a member of Environmental Institute of Kenyaand I highly believe I will use my knowledge and skills to bring impact to the society and the country at large.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your consideration. I look forward to your feedback and consideration for the opportunity.</p>\r\n<p>Yours Sincerely,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Joy Jepngetich Kibet</p>'),
