(5070, NULL, NULL, 5448, NULL, 'Associate', 'x', 'Kenyan', '35831338', '154 - 50400', 'Busia', 'Busia', '704766444', '<p>I am a seasoned Quality Assurance &amp; Compliance Lead with a strong background in managing Quality Management Systems (QMS). Leveraging my expertise, I have successfully overseen the development, implementation, and maintenance of ISO 9001 and ISO 17025 standards within organizations, ensuring the highest levels of quality and compliance.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to my role in quality assurance, I am also a dedicated environmentalist, registered as an associate expert. This registration with environmental authorities reflects my commitment to sustainable practices and environmental stewardship. By seamlessly integrating my skills in QMS management with my passion for environmentalism, I bring a unique perspective that contributes to both operational excellence and ecological responsibility. I am enthusiastic about creating a harmonious balance between quality assurance and environmental sustainability in every aspect of my professional journey.</p>'),
