(5329, '2024-05-31 12:41:41', '2024-05-31 12:41:41', 5739, NULL, 'Lead', 'stephanieojee@gmail.com', 'Kenya', '32730040', 'Nairobi 00100', 'Nairobi', 'Nairobi', '0717207825', 'Experienced and dedicated professional with experience in diverse areas aligned environmental assessment and management. I have actively contributed to natural resource management, environmental conservation, rehabilitation of arid environments, and project planning and management. My expertise encompasses program coordination and execution, field-work and research, monitoring and evaluation, strategic communication and collaboration, data collection and analysis, community mobilization, capacity building, and expertise make me a valuable asset'),
